data.description: CORNER LOT WITH 3 BED, 2 BATH DOUBLE WIDE HOME! Lots of great features in this property including an open and inviting floor plan.  Living area features sky lights, vaulted ceilings and open feel.  Kitchen features lots of storage and cabinet space There is a spacious island and plenty of room to eat in the dining room.  Main bedroom has vaulted ceilings,  large closet and dual vanities in the bathroom.  Outside, the yard is fully landscaped with easy care desert. Carport, Patio and storage sheds too!
